      "content": "hey i need to talk to someone about something weird. i think i'm seeing things before they actually happen. like, i saw this specific cracked coffee mug at a cafe this morning and it felt... heavy? like it was vibrating. then ten mins later on the news i saw a report about a massive earthquake in a place i've never even been. it's like the mug was an echo of the event. am i losing it or is this actually happening?",
